title.rendered: Fashion Beauty Editorial “FABulous Beauty” for Fab UK magazine

content.rendered:
Beautiful model Felicie rocking Spring inspired look for Fab UK, wearing jewelry by French jeweler Burma Paris, dressed in Farhad Re!


Below is a full look; dress and bag by Parisian Haute Couture designer Farhad Re SS21, jewelry by French jeweler Burma Paris.


Healthy glow, natural make up, full brows and subtle elegance is what Spring 2021 is all about!

Credits;

Beauty Editorial FABulous Beauty

Photographer: Christina V Henningstad @christina_henningstad Model: Felicie - UpModels @upmodelsparis

Stylist: Antoine Schmidt @antoineschmidtvb

Makeup: Serguei Chatel @serguei.chatel

MUAH: Camille Laura Boudet @kaambdt @campusdesmaquilleurs Production: Fashionview @fashionview.eu

Retoucher: Anna Gruzdova @retoucher_anna.g

Location: Millennium Hotel Paris Opera @millenniumopera

Wardrobe Credits:

Black Dress - NATAN

Jewelry - BURMA

Green Dress - NATAN

Golden Bag - FARHAD RE

Golden Crown - GEORGES MAKAROUN COUTURE White Dress - FARHAD RE

Black Bag - FARHAD RE Lipstick - EYMARD GABRIELLE

Thanks Mephistopheles Productions & Caroline Charles Communication
